race.comment: WHISKEY MCGRAW (2) is having first try over this longer journey. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 9 lengths (25.71) at Q Lakeside. Looks well placed and should feature. MIDNIGHT QUEEN (8) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when fourth (25.44) in a OPEN at Q Lakeside. Can improve sharply here. JAVEN'S SHOT (1) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame at her last four runs, the latest finishing second (19.93) at Capalaba. Expecting another good run. Something for the Multiples: ALL OUT FIRE (6)
